1. A random word will be assigned from the list of words avaiable 
2. Player needs to guess the letters one by one 
3. If the player guesses the right letter then it will be filled at the correct places 
4. If the player guesses the wrong letter then number of attempts will be deducted and hangman image will start getting constructed 
5. With every incorrect guess one step of hangman image will be made and one attempt will be reduced 
6. Player needs to guess the word before they run out of attempts or before the entire image of hangman is created 
Note: (You can customize the number of attempts and the words present in the list )
